rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0001
rows.name: Boy, have you lost your mind?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0002
rows.name:
You know damn well what that data means to us—
to our entire race![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0003
rows.name: Of course I do—it means an end to this giant lie.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0003_2
rows.name: I've been waiting a long time for this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0004
rows.name: [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0005
rows.name: Commander, what's going on?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0006
rows.name: Ask Lao.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0007
rows.name: We caught him stealing a data terminal with classified intel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0008
rows.name: Stealing intel?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0009
rows.name: Explain yourself, Lao![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0010
rows.name: [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0010_2
rows.name: You should've let me die that day, Elma.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0011
rows.name: You knew the truth—that I was a Ganglion spy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0012
rows.name: What?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0013
rows.name: I had my suspicions. But I didn't want to believe it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0014
rows.name: Your mistake.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0015
rows.name:
And it'll cost you.
The data, and your newest Skell, the Prog Ares.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0016
rows.name: The Ganglion'll appreciate the gift.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0017
rows.name:
Boy, I am going to kick your ass so hard,
your real body will feel it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0018
rows.name: Not if you value your precious data.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0019
rows.name: Lao, what the hell is going on here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0020
rows.name:
Oh, look at this—the whole gang's
coming out to say good-bye.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0021
rows.name: What the hell, Lao?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0022
rows.name:
Hold your fire!
He's got the only copy of that data on his mim.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0023
rows.name: Dammit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0024
rows.name: A little insurance policy. Sorry, Doug.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0025
rows.name: You'd betray all your friends? Your entire species?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0026
rows.name:
I'm no big fan of theirs, believe me—
the talking cats OR that giant leech.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0027
rows.name: But the Ganglion and I share a common goal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0028
rows.name: And that is?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0029
rows.name: Think about it, Doug. You know the answer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0030
rows.name: The hell I do! You've lost it, man.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0031
rows.name: Yeah...I lost it all. Good-bye.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11020100_MSG0032
rows.name: Lao![ST:wait ]
